{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Isa|6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","chapter":6,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":1,"text":"In the year that King Uzziah died, I saw the Lord seated on a high and lofty throne, and the hem of his robe filled the temple.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":2,"text":"Seraphim were standing above him; they each had six wings: with two they covered their faces, with two they covered their feet, and with two they flew.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":3,"text":"And one called to another:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":4,"text":"The foundations of the doorways shook at the sound of their voices, and the temple was filled with smoke.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":5,"text":"Then I said:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":6,"text":"Then one of the seraphim flew to me, and in his hand was a glowing coal that he had taken from the altar with tongs.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":7,"text":"He touched my mouth with it and said:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":8,"text":"Then I heard the voice of the Lord asking:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":9,"text":"And he replied:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":10,"text":"Make the minds of these people dull;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":11,"text":"Then I said, “Until when, Lord?” And he replied:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":12,"text":"and the Lord drives the people far away,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","bookOrder":22,"chapter":6,"verse":13,"text":"Though a tenth will remain in the land,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Isa","chapter":6,"paragraphStarts":[1,4,5,6,8,9,10,11,12,13],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Isaiah’s Call and Mission"}],"poetryBlocks":[{"beforeVerse":10,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":12,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":13,"level":1}],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:6:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In the year that King Uzziah "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 15:1","book":"2Ki","chapter":15,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 1:1","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 14:28","book":"Isa","chapter":14,"verse":28,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" died, I saw the Lord "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 32:30","book":"Gen","ch